          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-06-25 09:17:30" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>one who has the responsibility of caring for spiritual concerns</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>one responsible for</Gloss>
                <Gloss>one who cares for</Gloss>
                <Gloss>guardian</Gloss>
                <Gloss>keeper</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In {S:06000202500026} ἐπίσκοπος is applied to Christ, and it no doubt shares certain of the meanings associated with ἐπίσκοπος[b] in {D:53.71}, but the focus in {S:06000202500026} is not upon leadership but upon the role of caring for the believers.</Comments>
